701281f-a.title: Bronx: Home Street - Intervale Street
701281f-a.text:
Home Street (right), north side, east from Intervale Avenue,
showing the Holy Trinity Lutheran Church, at the N.E. corner of the
aforementioned thoroughfares. On the left is the east side of Inter-
vale Avenue, extending north to Fox Street.
April 26, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
